01:02:32,440 --> 01:02:34,060
It's not like that.

763
01:02:34,060 --> 01:02:36,180
Okay, then. Look at me.

764
01:02:36,180 --> 01:02:37,640
Look at me.

765
01:02:37,640 --> 01:02:39,430
It's okay.

